name: once in a life time V2

metadata.name: 29-year-old me #1/3
metadata.description:
I am 30 now. 

how many new you have you met in your life 

how many old you have you let go 

You will find 29 bodies of me in this series of "29-year-old me" to cerebrate my survival of 3 decades in this society or whatever you name

let the healing process of some shame you have done to yourself
